# =======================================================================
# Additional Notes
# =======================================================================
# This .gitignore prioritizes security by preventing:
# 1. Environment files with actual secrets (.env, .env.local, etc.)
# 2. SSL certificates and private keys (*.key, *.pem, *.crt)
# 3. Generated Kubernetes secrets (kubernetes/secrets-*.yaml)
# 4. Ansible vault passwords and SSH keys
# 5. Any files containing "secret" or "password" in their names
#
# Safe to commit:
# - .env.example (template with placeholders)
# - kubernetes/secrets-*.yaml.example (example manifests)
# - Documentation and configuration templates
